{"tid":562293,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該年宵班人唔好恃住件貨品係本土設計就奉旨要人買","createTime":"2018-02-15T18:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T02:46:15.000Z","uid":5588,"like":154,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f38e9079931f99ca17da3efcdd741f1fef33d5f4","tid":562293,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:26:02.000Z","msg":"本來今年行年宵都冇乜嘢，見到觀塘有檔真係把鬼火<br />\n<br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條友：你哋睇吓呢個袋，係咪覺得應該要帶佢返屋企呢？<br />\n我：唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友再講咗輪我都冇理佢，點知突然<br />\n條友：<span style=\"color: red;\">你係咪香港人？！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友：香港人係咪應該要支持番香港人先？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：下 關咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（你個袋我買黎都冇撚用 點解要買？）<br />\n條友：我哋呢到嘅嘢全部都同香港有關，你應該要支持我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本想同佢嘈，但人多同埋同行仲有人，所以吞咗佢當聽唔到咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係，唔好覺得香港人一定要奉旨支持<span style=\"color: red;\">所有</span>香港設計嘅野<br />\n香港有人設計，有人賣一啲有創意嘅野固然值得欣賞<br />\n但係我哋都係消費者，買嘢都要睇自己啱唔啱用㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果嗰樣物品啱用嘅話，當然會優先支持本土製作，但係唔啱使/設計到好垃圾嘅嘢，唔該你哋唔好劈頭問一句「你係咪香港人」就想人幫襯你，講到唔支持你就唔係香港人咁，好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你哋係滯銷嘅話，唔係應該怪香港人，而係應該檢討吓係咪你地設計有問題，或者賣嘅嘢唔等使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發洩完 多謝收睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98e40383c86fc529eb2a553a4557594443d38f3","tid":562293,"uid":77788,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"246f811dd9eff9693fb404c5173810419d8118b2","tid":562293,"uid":133518,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"好多人消費本土"},{"pid":"c158ec983598d7d8a3e746f06483ad683a550756","tid":562293,"uid":7954,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf618e55372b5791c59523fe5f4b0f93ea7c7b76","tid":562293,"uid":88862,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:43:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27c04679a5c10c4fa4df77cd66269fb2ce4dc953","tid":562293,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"有好多都係求鳩其諗啲自以爲好笑嘅字句落case/袋到 就覺得自己好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76d0fee3e9f5bc0ca4c7574a40094136bbde8f5","tid":562293,"uid":135866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":